Class MainScreen

java.lang.Object
controller.MainScreen
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class MainScreen extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
Controller class where the user manages customers and appointments. In this screen the user can add/modify/delete customers and appointments. User can also access a report.
